<title>Adam Khawitak A Um?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Maa ei suontu bul-Evi leh Adam chuh,
 Eden huon hawih a Lalpa'n a kawihte kha;
 Nichenga lawp leh kipak a len lai un,
 Sapna huoise tak mai chu a za tau.

[V2]
 &quot;Adam khawitaka um?
 Aw khawia um a na him?
 Sun ninem tieng kipakin I kipawl seka.
 Bang dinga tu a ei kiselsan na hi tam&quot;?
 Pathien na mansak tai,
 Aw Adam khawi a um?

[V3]
 2. Dawnna Aw a hung gii, thavai leh ling kawm in,
 Aw Lalpa Pathien Na mel vak ka muh un;
 Sangawn a um ka hih uh ka kihe dawk un,
 Lau leh lingin ka hun kisel san tau.

[V4]
 3. Aw suopih deihtak, tuhin khawiah na um em?
 Lalpa Pathien in tuhin a hun dawng hi;
 Sapna pawimawh tak hi bangti'n na dawng ta die ?
 Na Pathien kisel mangsan ding na him?

[V5]
 4. Keile Lalpa Pathien sangawn a um ka hi,
 Tih ka kihet in Na kawm lam ka hun zuon;
 Na zahngaihna mi gilote Na piek sek kha,
 Ei ngaidam in Aw kei migilo hih.</lyrics>
</song>